 Fuse Chan Sathorn Duplex 2 Bedroom
 2 Bedroom Duplex Unit at Fuse Chan Sathorn Condo now available for Rent at 28,000 Baht/Month for a minimum one year contract.
 

 This 2 Bedroom Duplex Unit is 56 Sq.m of well used space. The unit comes fully furnished to a high standard and has a modern design and layout. Lower floor consists of the living room, dining area, and kitchen that is fully equipped with top brand name appliances. Upper floor has the 2 bedrooms both with high quality bedding and built in wardrobes and shelves. This unit is located on a middle floor with a beautiful view of the swimming pool.
 

 Fuse Chan Sathorn is a condominium project, developed by Pruksa Real Estate, located at Chan Sathorn. Construction of Fuse condo was completed in 2015. Condominium comprises of 3 buildings, having 31floors.
 

 Facilities include a large infinity edge swimming pool with spacious sundeck, Fully equipped fitness room with view of the pool and city, sauna and steam rooms, changing rooms, modern styled grand lobby, landscaped garden, childrenтАЩs playground, mail boxes, function room, and a library. Other amenities include high speed elevators, 24 hour security, keycard system in place, and CCTV.
 

 Located in a excellent location on Chan Rd, easy access to the rest of Bangkok. Convenience stores can be found just minutes walk away. Schools and kindergarten can be reached in just 10 minutes
